      </a>

  </div>


    <section id="moduledoc">
<p>Distributed test execution control for <code class="inline">Common Test</code>.</p><p>This module exports functions for running <code class="inline">Common Test</code> nodes on multiple hosts
in parallel.</p>
    </section>

</div>

