  <section class="docstring">



<p>Gets a reference to the <code class="inline">Common Test</code> master event manager. The reference can be
used to, for example, add a user-specific event handler while tests are running.</p><p><em>Example:</em></p><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="nc">gen_event</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">add_handler</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0212520809-1">(</span><span class="nc">ct_master</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">get_event_mgr_ref</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0212520809-2">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0212520809-2">)</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="ss">my_ev_h</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="0212520809-3">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0212520809-3">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="0212520809-1">)</span></code></pre>
  </section>
</section>
